# Light client-side password gate. Treat as semi-secret — short passwords are
# brute-forceable from the hex hash in seconds. Leave unset to disable the gate.
#
# Generate from a password (macOS / Linux):
#   echo -n "your-password" | shasum -a 256 | cut -d' ' -f1
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (which is gitignored) and fill in the hash.
VITE_PASSWORD_HASH=
